attributes.content: Well if it ain't a Siracusan stray right here in my lounge. You're all outta crossbow bolts? And I'm still standin'?
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: So this is the Emperor. You come through a rain of arrows still holding your drink. Lucky bastard.
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: ...Lungmen isn't much for straight up, close-quarters fighting.
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: If you don't play by the rules, you get kicked out of the game.
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: Rules?
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: By the time the cops get here, all they're gonna find are your splattered corpses, Penguin Logistics.
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: ...it's all their people out there.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: They got the back covered too. Looks like this feller's mighty thorough.
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: That coward Capone is too afraid of the Rat King and Wei Yenwu, even if that one might need a thought or two...
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: But you and the Rat King? You ain't worth a second look.
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: Yeah? Is that really what you think? Or you just tryin' to sound scary?
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: I believe it with all my heart, 'Mr. Emperor.'
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: Croissant, grab me a bottle. Our friend here's got the broke brain. I'm gonna do him a favor and fix it up for him.
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: But baws, not for nothin', we already smashed a couple million Lungmen dollars' worth of booze over here.
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: ...and how much were their lives worth?
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: Don't see how it could add up to that much.
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: Are we doing this?
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Nah. We're keeping the deal we made with Lil Wei. We don't go all out in Lungmen, we don't make trouble, we don't threaten life and limb. Keep it professional. Business is business.
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: But we been on the run for a grand total of five hours today. That's double my normal work day. Double!
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: Not to mention we torched a whole year's worth of goodies! Cars, booze, and my precious vinyl!
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: And now we got some tragic, unanticipated deaths here in my club. What're we gonna do about all this? Hm?
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: Understood.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Texas. This name of yours displeases me.
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: I don't recall knowing any Siracusans like you. But you're about to go running out of Lungmen with your tail between your legs.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: You're gonna regret slandering my family, Texas.
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: Who here's the stray dog who ran off to Lungmen? You know the truth. You ain't fit to go toe to toe with a Sicilian.
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: That's a good face right, there, Texas! You almost look Siracusan like that!
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: Wow.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: This is a surprise. You got called out too?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: You could say that. But it's honestly a relief to get pulled away from those cocktail parties.
Hm. Does a small-time mafia dust-up really deserve such a grand response?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: No, it doesn't. But it makes for a nice excuse to tear myself away from troublesome social interactions.
Croissant has ordered a new custom accessory for her hammer. Exusiai has sought my help in caring for her beloved gun. In short, there is much to be done.
Yeah, I might have something for you too.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: No matter. Assisting my colleagues with such trivialities is one of my duties, in addition to my primary function.
Can you look after this staff for me?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: This white one. You do understand its significance, don't you?
Just for tonight. Let me relax a bit and enjoy the Carnival.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: I can't exactly take it out onto the dance floor with me. I'll lose control.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Of course. I will take it. It's my responsibility.
Heh. It always comes down to work, huh? Thanks anyway.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: You want to go for a drink afterwards? It's on me.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: I would love to. Socializing over drinks with colleagues is vastly more meaningful than the empty social niceties I've endured.
But I'm afraid, looking at these movements, it may be a challenge to save The Ends of the Earth.
...So, did you just get in to Lungmen? How much do you know about what's gone on tonight?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Everything. The threads that make up this year's Carnival are uncomplicated. The tapestry is abundantly clear to me.
Are you not going to help?
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: I am not. I will leave the physical labor to your youthful vigor, look after your items, enjoy a cup of tea, and wait for the situation to resolve itself.
Right then. The Rat King is waiting for you. Do please enjoy yourself.
You too, Yith.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: It's Sauin. It only comes once a year. Don't work yourself too hard.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: Anyway, I'm out.
attributes.name: Mostima

attributes.content: ...Sauin?
attributes.name: Yith

attributes.content: Oh my. I was supposed to take off for Sauin.
attributes.name: Yith

attributes.content: And here I am working overtime like always... what a dreadful waste.
attributes.name: Yith

attributes.content: But at least, now that she's entrusted you to me, we can reminisce about the good old days, my old friend.
attributes.name: Yith

attributes.content: Mm. It's nice to grip you in my hand like this. No complaining.
attributes.name: Yith

attributes.content: You have nowhere to run.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: *Pant pant* Texas, you got the skills to match your name... Your Family——
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: Shut up.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Texaaas~ I've taken out more than you~
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: But Texas is holding down their leader. That's gotta be worth at least three?
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: Wha? So I'm losing?
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: Naw. Nobody else is even countin'.
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: Oh, we still got a bottle over here. Lemme check the price tag.
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: That's one, two, three... seven! Seven zeroes! Thank you, Lady Luck!
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: What're you scared of? There's only five of 'em!
attributes.name: Mafioso

attributes.content: No cliches in my club, please!
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: Gah! My head... nng...
attributes.name: Mafioso

attributes.content: And you didn't even count me. There's six of us.
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: Six Penguin Logistics employees against an entire armed mob... and the logistics firm wins...?
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: ...that's kinda weird, isn't it?
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Ain't nothin' weird about that. When it comes to team fights, we're the best in Lungmen! Long as the numbers ain't too different.
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: Gah!
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: You lost. Give up.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Lost? Give up? Hah. Are you really THE 'Texas?'
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: When Sicilians cross swords, there ain't no winning or losing, there's only life or death.
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: You must regret not biting the bullet and finishing the job!
attributes.name: Gambino

attributes.content: Fire in the hole!
attributes.name: Mafioso

attributes.content: Grrr! Take cover!
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Aagh! Another bomb!
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: ...we let them get away again.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Should we go after them?
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: No. I may have underestimated them a bit.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Even if they're a bunch of losers who ran off to Lungmen, they're still Sicilian mobsters.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Texas, are you hurt?! L- let me take care of you.
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: It's not deep, don't worry.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: I'm worrying! Sit down. I'll get the first aid kit...
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: Sicilians... what's a Sicilian anyway? Is it a kind of Siracusan?
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: The Sicilian Union is one of the origins of Siracusa's Twelve Families. It was the first city to turn to violence to achieve its goals.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: It's where we get the word 'Sicilian' in Siracusan.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: But these days... the word has kind of a different meaning... it's pretty rare for a Siracusan to actually call herself a 'Sicilian.'
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: They're not as strong as they used to be... for a whole bunch of reasons. But if they still call themselves that... well...
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Breathe, Texas, breathe. You're wearing yourself out talking that much.
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: The main point is it's a way for wannabe dangerous mobsters to tell everybody they think they're dangerous mobsters, right?
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: ...yeah.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: We can't let them keep ambushing us like this. Our losses are only going to get worse.
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: We have to hit back, we need a...
attributes.name: Bison

attributes.content: Hold up. Just everybody hold the eff up. What excuse do you think I can give to my dumbass alcohol allergic bartender friend to explain what happened to his place?
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: Um... is there an explanation...?
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: At least the stool yer sittin' on's in great shape there, boss.
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: All we got left's one barstool?
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: Yes... that one barstool.
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: ...Aight. Broken bottles, shot up walls, and tattered velvet got its own unique vibe to it. Yeah. This is my new renovation, redecoratin' the joint!
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: Noooo way. Nobody's going to buy that.
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: We prob'ly just gotta pay him back for all the damages, huh? Aaagh. Looks like we're gonna hafta tighten our belts at Penguin Logistics fer a while.
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: Plus the whole place stinks of alcohol. And I'm all sticky. At least it's disinfecting my wounds.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Don't be stupid, you can't use wine as a disinfectant! Here, I've got some medical alcohol... why is there a straw? N- never mind. Here, Texas, let me apply it...
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: ...I had another idea.
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: If these punks gotta come at us on Sauin...
attributes.name: Emperor

attributes.content: Then we gotta send 'em peacefully to the afterlife.
attributes.name: Emperor
